{"tid":1542432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"北角懷疑出現持槍客","createTime":"2019-09-05T00:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T00:35:56.000Z","uid":65182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0b81c61af8a746c82aaf713bdc1805be67496235","tid":1542432,"uid":65182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:32:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190904&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60009965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190904%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60009965&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6rufY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=30d26b03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190904%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60009965&h=17276ce7\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190904&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60009965</a><br />\n<br />\n北角懷疑出現持槍客。傍晚6時許，有市民報案，指一部沿英皇道近明園西行對開行駛中的客貨車形迹可疑，懷疑司機持槍。警方接報後，在附近一帶兜截，終在建華街近堡壘街截停有關車輛，司機見狀將手槍拋出車外，警員一度拔槍戒備。警員其後拘捕該名司機，撿獲一把類似手槍的物體及一個彈匣，拘捕一名男子，他被黑布蒙頭、雙手反鎖坐於地上.........<br />\n<br />\n轉載蘋果日報"},{"pid":"3f6a04ac9dbba8581e2f7168f67a48a445b8487e","tid":1542432,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:35:56.000Z","msg":"[推比攬炒巴] 可唔可以眾籌比台灣義士？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542400</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}